{"TopicId":202022,"ForumId":109,"TopicTitle":"Will the Big-S rudder have airbrakes?","CreatedByName":"Wizard Kerbal","CreatedById":209063,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-27T02:46:04Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Wizard Kerbal","CreatedById":209063,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-27T02:46:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI really like shuttles. They\u0027re really fun to fly, and I love re-entering with space planes. BUT! I don\u0027t like having to clip to rudders together to get that airbrake. ANd on all my mark 3 space planes, I use that air brake technique even though it induces Z-fighting.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn KSP 2, or even an update in KSP 1, can we add air-brakes to it? It would be a really nice feature, even though it\u0027s a small one!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kernel Kraken","CreatedById":181383,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-27T18:59:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA good question to ask is \u0022Will there be a Big-S rudder in KSP 2?\u0022 I feel like it\u0027s a bit early to be asking about the features about specific parts. It\u0027s a really cool idea, though!\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NutellaSandwich","CreatedById":207876,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-27T19:06:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223961919\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022202022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221619549960\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022181383\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kernel Kraken\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 minutes ago, Kernel Kraken said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWill there be a Big-S rudder in KSP 2?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI remember that someone at Intercept Games said that all parts from the original game would be in KSP2, although I may be wrong.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"PlutoISaPlanet","CreatedById":206057,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-27T19:08:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223961922\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022202022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221619550413\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022207876\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022NutellaSandwich\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, NutellaSandwich said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI remember that someone at Intercept Games said that all parts from the original game would be in KSP2, although I may be wrong.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMost if not all\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dr. Kerbal","CreatedById":207217,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-27T22:20:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI like this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"PlutoISaPlanet","CreatedById":206057,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-27T22:52:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:happy:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/happy.png\u0022 title=\u0022:happy:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223962018\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022202022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221619562019\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022207217\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Dr. Kerbal\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n31 minutes ago, Dr. Kerbal said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI like this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SpaceFace545","CreatedById":196943,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-27T23:05:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe maybe not. Its way too early and futile to inquire about what parts will be in the game and what capabilities they will have.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}